Map {
User Stories {
Display Unsupported Orders: As a user, I want to be able to view all orders that are not supported by the running application.

Select Travel Time: As a user, I want to be able to select the amount of time I want to spend running.

Track Progress: As a user, I want to be able to track my progress while running.

Set Goals: As a user, I want to be able to set goals for my running sessions.

View Stats: As a user, I want to be able to view my running stats such as distance, time, and calories burned.

Share Progress: As a user, I want to be able to share my progress with friends and family.

Receive Notifications: As a user, I want to be able to receive notifications when I reach certain milestones.

}

Design {
Create User Interface: As a designer, I want to create an intuitive user interface for the running application.

Design Navigation: As a designer, I want to design a navigation system that is easy to use and understand.

Design Visuals: As a designer, I want to design visuals that are visually appealing and engaging.

Test Application: As a designer, I want to test the application to ensure it is functioning properly.

}

Development {
Develop Backend: As a developer, I want to develop the backend of the running application.

Integrate APIs: As a developer, I want to integrate APIs into the running application.

Debug Code: As a developer, I want to debug the code to ensure it is functioning properly.

Implement Features: As a developer, I want to implement features that will enhance the user experience.

}
}
